Qn.9. Write a Java Program to Print 1 To 10 Without Using Loop. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public class Main
{
    public static void printNum(int num){
        if(num<=10)
        {
            System.out.println(num);
            printNum(num+1);
        }
    }
    
	public static void main(String[] args) {
	    
	printNum(1);
	}
}
